rmation cannot be completely accessed as long as it does not happen that\nall parties are together. As an application, we connect our sets with local\ninformation hiding in multipartite system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2022 07:53:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2022 04:46:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Jan 2023 01:29:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2023 08:10:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-27"}
