 from capillary effect, which was an interplay between the\ninterfacial tension and wettability. Paring these two parameters by formulating\nimbibing brine to anticipate high oil recovery is crucial and of challenge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2022 08:30:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-16"}
