ts, while ROLAND can easily scale to dynamic graphs with 56\nmillion edges. After re-implementing these baselines using the ROLAND training\nstrategy, ROLAND models still achieve on average 15.5% relative MRR improvement\nover the baselines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2022 14:51:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-16"}
